<template>
  <v-checkbox
    v-for="user in users"
    :key="user.id"
    v-model="selectedUsers"
    :label="user.name"
  />
</template>

<script>
import { mapState } from 'vuex'

export default {
  computed: {
    ...mapState(['users'])
  },
  data() {
    return {
      selectedUsers: []
    }
  },
  methods: {
    async submitUsersToAPI() {
      const response = await axios.post('/api/users', {
        users: this.selectedUsersrails
      })
    }
  }
}
</script>
